
                  HUSKYLIB license notes.

HUSKYLIB is a part of The HUSKY Fidonet Software project,
see http://husky.sourceforge.net for details.

Initially HUSKYLIB compose from sources moved from two libraries:
"SMAPI; Modified Squish MSGAPI" and "FIDOCONFIG - library for fidonet configs".

FIDOCONFIG a licensed on LGPL.

Squish MSGAPI0 is copyright 1991 by Scott J. Dudley on own public domain
license.

In 2003 year Scott J. Dudley agree to change SMAPI license to LGPL and now
HUSKYLIB license is following:

